k (PM, repairs, contracts). Pros can bid immediately.</p><div class=\"mb-4 p-3 bg-[var(--gold-glow)] rounded text-sm\"><a class=\"font-semibold text-[var(--gold)]\" href=\"/signup/owner\">Sign up as Owner</a> or <a class=\"text-[var(--gold)] underline\" href=\"/login\">sign in</a> to post live needs.</div><form class=\"space-y-4\"><div><label class=\"label\">Facility / Practice Name *</label><input class=\"input\" required=\"\" placeholder=\"Your Med Spa or Hospital\" disabled=\"\" value=\"\"/></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3\"><div><label class=\"label\">City</label><input class=\"input\" placeholder=\"Phoenix\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label class=\"label\">State</label><input class=\"input\" placeholder=\"AZ\" value=\"\"/></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3\"><div><label class=\"label\">Service Type</label><select class=\"select\"><option value=\"PM\" selected=\"\">PM</option><option value=\"Emergency Repair\">Emergency Repair</option><option value=\"Install / Commission\">Install / Commission</option><option value=\"Calibration\">Calibration</option><option value=\"Full Contract\">Full Contract</option><option value=\"Other\">Other</option></select></div><div><label class=\"label\">Urgency</label><select class=\"select\"><option value=\"Low\">Low</option><option value=\"Medium\" selected=\"\">Medium</option><option value=\"High\">High</option><option value=\"Emergency\">Emergency</option></select></div></div><div><label class=\"label\">Laser Model (if known)</label><select class=\"select\"><option value=\"\" selected=\"\">— Any / Not specified —</option><option value=\"PowerSuite\">PowerSuite 100W Holmium</option><option value=\"MedLite C6\">MedLite C6 / IV</option><option value=\"AcuPulse Duo\">AcuPulse Duo CO₂</option><option value=\"Aura\">AURA XP 15W KTP</option><option value=\"Iridex\">Oculight / Cyclo G6</option><option value=\"Sphinx Jr\">Sphinx Junior 30W</option><option value=\"OmniGuide\">InteliGuide CO₂ 25W</option><option value=\"